column5: Hi,I'm looking for different individuals to fish with on Long Lake. I'm looking to gain experience; I fish 4 days a week and have my own boat (lund pro v 1900) so I'm not a free loader. Just looking for experence fisherman to share their knowledge with a newbie.If interested call William @ 729-4017 (Sask)ThanksWilliam
